data.title: Scratch Labels Manufacturer from Kolkata India
meta_keywords: Best Scratch Labels Manufacturer in Kolkata India
data.meta_description: At PB Holotech, we are the top Scratch Label manufacturer from Kolkata, India. We offer Scratch Labels made with fine polymer plastic films and customisation.
data.text: We offer Scratch Labels at a wide range. This is made up of fine polymer plastic films chosen from a diverse range of plastics with the extended support of skilled professionals. Out of two sides of the label, one side is concealed with latex. To find out what is hidden, the user has to scratch the covering substance.
